10:39.000 --> 10:41.000
a couple of chicks. One was asian.

10:41.400 --> 10:42.500
Kinda hot.

10:43.400 --> 10:46.100
Okay, so you're telling me
that you saw all of them

10:46.100 --> 10:48.700
–In the park last night, right?
–Yep.

10:51.400 --> 10:53.000
