11:35.100 --> 11:37.600
Donny was out of control.
We were just trying to stop him.

11:37.600 --> 11:39.100
Why don't I believe you?

11:44.200 --> 11:45.800
Guys, just tell the truth.

11:51.700 --> 11:53.400
Sometimes we'd go to the park, too.

11:54.600 --> 11:56.700
