messed up, and he's got this gun.

12:14.300 --> 12:17.700
And he— And he's— He's yelling
at donny, "where's my money?

12:17.700 --> 12:20.900
I need my friggin' money!”
Donny owes him 200 bucks.

12:20.900 --> 12:22.700
–Donny didn't have it.
–Then the guy points the gun.

12:22.700 --> 12:26.200
